walk to the bathroom

high_descs: Go to the left end of the table just ahead of you, where the cutting board is.
Pick up the butter knife from the cutting board.
Look to the red couch on the other side of the room and go in the door just next to it, then go straight and take two rights into the bathroom.
Slice the banana that's in the bathroom sink.
Go back to the area with the table and microwave and go to the fridge to the left of them.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Return to the sink with the banana.
Pick up one banana slice.
Go back to the fridge you put the knife in.
Put the banana slice in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Look back towards the table you first got the knife from.
Put the banana slice down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a refrigerated banana slice on a table.

high_descs: Walk to the left side of the wood table in front of you, to the cutting board on the corner.
Pick up the butter knife sitting on the board.
Turn to the red couch against the wall, then enter the door just next to it, and then take a right into the bathroom.
Slice the banana that's in the sink.
Go back to the table you got the knife from and turn to the fridge beside it.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go back to the sink with the banana.
Pick up one slice of the banana.
Go back to the fridge.
Cool the banana slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn back to the table you got the knife from.
Put the banana slice down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled banana slice on a table.
